<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #F59E0B; color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .content { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
        .footer { background-color: #333; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 20px; border-radius: 8px; }
        .pending-box { background-color: #FEF3C7; border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
        .info-box { background-color: #E0F2FE; border-left: 4px solid #3B82F6; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
        .button { display: inline-block; background-color: #F59E0B; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; font-weight: bold; }
        .button:hover { background-color: #D97706; }
        .details { background-color: white; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; }
        .details p { margin: 8px 0; }
        .icon { font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .timeline { background-color: white; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; }
        .timeline-item { display: flex; margin: 10px 0; padding: 10px; background-color: #F9FAFB; border-radius: 4px; }
        .timeline-icon { margin-right: 15px; font-size: 24px; }
        .timeline-content { flex: 1; }
        .status-badge { display: inline-block; background-color: #FEF3C7; color: #92400E; padding: 5px 15px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="icon">⏳</div>
            <h1 style="margin: 0;">KYC Verification Under Review</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello {{organizationName}},</p>

            <div class="pending-box">
                <h2 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #92400E;">Manual Review Required</h2>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0; font-size: 16px;">Your KYC (Know Your Customer) verification requires additional manual review by our compliance team. We appreciate your patience during this process.</p>
                <p style="margin: 15px 0 5px 0;">
                    <span class="status-badge">PENDING REVIEW</span>
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="details">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1F2937;">Application Details</h3>
                <p><strong>Organization:</strong> {{organizationName}}</p>
                <p><strong>Application ID:</strong> {{applicationId}}</p>
                <p><strong>Submission Date:</strong> {{submittedDate}}</p>
                <p><strong>Current Status:</strong> Under Manual Review</p>
                {{#if estimatedReviewTime}}
                <p><strong>Estimated Review Time:</strong> {{estimatedReviewTime}}</p>
                {{/if}}
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1E40AF;">Why Manual Review?</h3>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;">Some applications require additional human verification to ensure accuracy and compliance. This is a standard procedure and doesn't indicate any issues with your application.</p>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0;">Common reasons include:</p>
                <ul style="margin: 10px 0;">
                    <li>Document clarity requiring expert assessment</li>
                    <li>Complex business structures</li>
                    <li>International documents needing verification</li>
                    <li>Routine quality assurance checks</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1F2937;">Review Process Timeline</h3>

                <div class="timeline-item" style="background-color: #D1FAE5;">
                    <div class="timeline-icon">✓</div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <strong>Application Submitted</strong>
                        <p style="margin: 5px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6B7280;">Your documents have been received</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="timeline-item" style="background-color: #D1FAE5;">
                    <div class="timeline-icon">✓</div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <strong>Automated Checks Complete</strong>
                        <p style="margin: 5px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6B7280;">Initial verification passed</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="timeline-item" style="background-color: #FEF3C7; border: 2px solid #F59E0B;">
                    <div class="timeline-icon">⏳</div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <strong>Manual Review (Current Stage)</strong>
                        <p style="margin: 5px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #92400E;">Compliance team reviewing your application</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-icon">○</div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <strong>Final Decision</strong>
                        <p style="margin: 5px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6B7280;">You'll receive notification via email</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div style="background-color: #F3F4F6; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1F2937;">What Happens Next?</h3>
                <ul style="margin: 10px 0;">
                    <li>Our compliance team will carefully review your submitted documents</li>
                    <li>You'll receive an email notification once the review is complete</li>
                    <li>If additional information is needed, we'll contact you directly</li>
                    <li>Most reviews are completed within 1-3 business days</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{statusUrl}}" class="button">Check Application Status</a>
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px; background-color: #E0F2FE; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; border-left: 4px solid #3B82F6;">
                <strong>No Action Required</strong><br>
                You don't need to do anything at this time. We'll notify you as soon as the review is complete. If we need any additional information, we'll reach out to you directly.
            </p>

            <p style="margin-top: 20px;">Thank you for your patience. We're committed to ensuring a thorough and secure verification process.</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #6B7280; font-size: 14px;">
                Best regards,<br>
                <strong>The Broxiva Compliance Team</strong>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Broxiva</strong> - Secure E-Commerce Platform</p>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0;">Questions? Contact us at {{supportEmail}}</p>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0;">&copy; {{currentYear}} Broxiva. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0; font-size: 11px;">
                This is an automated notification. Please do not reply to this email.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
